Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.15,0:00:13.48,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,A little to the right. Lower...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.87,0:00:22.84,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Saint Paulia School Festival
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.91,0:00:25.67,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,St. Paulia Academy's festival\Nis almost here.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.48,0:00:30.68,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Our school has a little ritual\Nthat has become a tradition.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.87,0:00:39.77,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Tada! Feast your eyes.\NThis is Mikami's locker key.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.94,0:00:42.38,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Really? The real thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.32,0:00:44.84,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna hang it up on the roof.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.05,0:00:47.71,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Meimi, what's this about a lock?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.90,0:00:51.16,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,It's a charm.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.33,0:00:54.30,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Honestly Seira, you're so dense\Nwhen it comes to things like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.24,0:00:58.90,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Okay? If there's a boy you like,\Nyou get hold of his lock...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.35,0:01:01.75,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,then attach it to the fence\Non the east side of the roof...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.02,0:01:06.36,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,then, at the festival's finale,\Nthat boy will ask you to dance.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.93,0:01:10.49,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,So that's why that fence\Nis covered with locks.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.77,0:01:15.61,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,That's right. It proves that you have\Nhis feelings locked to yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.69,0:01:21.45,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,The big problem is how to get\Nthe lock there in the first place.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.30,0:01:25.79,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Ryoko, please, please\Nask Yamamoto for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.01,0:01:27.97,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,What? No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.28,0:01:30.44,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Hey, I've got the curtain!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.06,0:01:38.96,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,I wonder if he's\Nalready given his lock to someone.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.67,0:01:44.80,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Asuka, put your leg in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.05,0:01:46.81,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,What for? Like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.08,0:01:48.61,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Heave!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.75,0:01:50.74,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Hey! What are you guys doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.36,0:01:56.06,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Junior in a bag, ready to go!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.37,0:01:59.43,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Do you think doing this kind\Nof thing to someone is funny?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.15,0:02:02.48,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,I guess I have\Nnothing to worry about.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.86,0:02:09.05,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,The Scoop Picture Causes\NTrouble at the School Fair
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.72,0:02:22.81,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Is anything troubling you?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.56,0:02:25.42,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,You can tell me if you like.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.68,0:02:35.31,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Miss Mimori... I mean, sister,\Nhave you heard?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.09,0:02:39.08,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,About how to get a partner\Nfor the festival's dance party?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.79,0:02:41.78,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Oh that, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.63,0:02:44.69,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Lucky, I just heard about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.41,0:02:52.24,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,A friend of mine asked me\Nto get this boy's lock for her today.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.12,0:02:59.55,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,But when I went to talk to him, Sawatari\Nfrom the school paper took our picture.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.13,0:03:14.06,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Sawatari!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.27,0:03:16.76,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, that shot was okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.58,0:03:20.07,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Sawatari, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.38,0:03:25.35,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,What are you going\Nto do with that picture?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.82,0:03:29.22,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Put it in the school paper, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.37,0:03:35.80,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,I'll call it 'The Trading of Love Tokens'.\NHow's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.65,0:03:40.05,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,You can't do that.\NI was only doing a favor for a friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.69,0:03:44.65,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,That won't show on the picture,\Nso it's not my problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.07,0:03:47.00,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,You can't...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.54,0:03:54.45,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,The problem is,\NI already have a boyfriend.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.79,0:03:58.98,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,If that picture is published,\Nit'll cause a huge misunderstanding.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.77,0:04:05.07,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,That's terrible.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.24,0:04:10.14,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Sawatari is that guy who will\Ndo anything for a story, isn't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.46,0:04:16.15,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,He's also quite popular\Nwith the girls in the school...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.50,0:04:20.83,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Yes, I know. I hope there's some way\Nwe can get that film from him.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.84,0:04:23.50,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Alright, I'm all fired up!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.98,0:04:27.18,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,St. Tail will teach that enemy\Nof girls a lesson!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.79,0:04:32.35,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,The big problem is,\Nwe don't have much time.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.80,0:04:37.03,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Can you send your challenge out\Nbefore he develops the pictures?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.44,0:04:38.41,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.44,0:04:40.20,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,But when will be a\Ngood time to do the job?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.35,0:04:41.71,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Let's see.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.95,0:04:46.05,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,The Festival is the day after tomorrow.\NAll the students will be staying late.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.89,0:04:50.23,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Everyone's free to wear\Na costume during the festival.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.47,0:04:52.46,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,That should be the perfect day.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.24,0:04:54.14,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.98,0:05:00.71,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,It wouldn't look suspicious to see\None or two people dressed as St. Tail.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.39,0:05:03.72,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.00,0:05:07.13,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.40,0:05:10.37,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,A St. Tail costume?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.98,0:05:13.61,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,That's right! See!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.02,0:05:18.85,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,We made it for you because, being so\Nathletic, you're perfect for the part!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.06,0:05:20.22,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Now wait a minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.30,0:05:22.73,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Let's rehearse for tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.80,0:05:24.43,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,You're right. Let's dress her!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.61,0:05:26.60,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,And your hair has\Ngot to be in a ponytail!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.71,0:05:27.87,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Hold it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.95,0:05:29.44,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Relax, just relax.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.75,0:05:31.65,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,This is just plain silly.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.56,0:05:33.35,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Don't fidget.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.92,0:05:35.76,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,You girls! You have got to be joking.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.23,0:05:39.03,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,You're ruining the image of St. Tail!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.57,0:05:41.13,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,What did you say?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.78,0:05:45.04,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,What exactly did you mean by that?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.12,0:05:47.02,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Exactly what it sounded like.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.35,0:05:48.82,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,How rude!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.23,0:05:56.13,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,And I thought I'd\Nget a cute shot of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.24,0:05:59.61,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,But I think that big piece of junk\Ngot in the picture, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.98,0:06:03.14,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Don't refer to me as a piece of junk!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.09,0:06:05.52,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,It's Sawatari, now is my chance!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.69,0:06:09.49,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Oh well.\NHere, a present for you anyhow.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.31,0:06:15.17,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,This is...!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.21,0:06:20.38,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,"I will come to the\Nschool festival to take Sawatari's film."
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.12,0:06:22.96,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,It's a challenge from St. Tail.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.16,0:06:25.15,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Really? You're kidding.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.47,0:06:32.60,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,A big piece of junk in the way, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.09,0:06:37.52,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Journalism Club
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.19,0:06:40.13,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,You're a real pest, aren't you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.77,0:06:43.63,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,St. Tail says she's\Ncoming for your film...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.81,0:06:47.17,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,I can protect my own stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.85,0:06:52.72,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,You think I'd trust the guy\Nwho keeps letting St. Tail get away?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.43,0:06:56.55,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,I'm not giving up!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.35,0:07:06.28,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,You're always trying to be\Nthe center of attention.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.55,0:07:08.52,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,You're beneath my concern, Asuka.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.74,0:07:19.37,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,For the time being,\NI've got to hide the film someplace.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.88,0:07:22.18,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,I guess the locker\Nshould be okay for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.30,0:07:29.13,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Sawatari!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.11,0:07:34.51,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Hey, what are you all doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.38,0:07:37.61,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,We'd like to have your lock.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.05,0:07:42.28,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Gee, sorry, but I only have one.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.70,0:07:45.86,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,That's okay! We bought you some!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.24,0:07:46.83,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.00,0:07:48.20,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,There!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.51,0:07:50.37,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Put these on his locker.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.78,0:07:52.54,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Just a moment, and...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.82,0:07:56.18,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,your new locks!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.96,0:07:59.66,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Sawatari\NWhat is this...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.23,0:08:03.39,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,And don't you dare take them off!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.54,0:08:07.17,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,I don't think I have a choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.41,0:08:08.94,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,We'll come take them off later.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.16,0:08:15.49,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,They shouldn't make\Nso many of these things!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.30,0:08:20.67,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Darn! This is stupid! Where am\NI gonna hide this film?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.59,0:08:28.21,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Asuka
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.89,0:08:31.52,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Boy, Asuka sure is careless.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.77,0:08:33.76,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Wait a minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.87,0:08:36.43,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Maybe I'll stash the film in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.04,0:08:39.94,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,I doubt any of the\Ngirls would want his lock.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.62,0:08:42.61,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,It's probably safer in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.16,0:08:44.71,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing there?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.56,0:08:47.43,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Isn't that Asuka's locker?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.23,0:08:51.23,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,I... well... it's not...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.48,0:08:58.54,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Why did you do that?!\NNow it's locked!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.65,0:09:01.75,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Why did you do that?!\NNow I can't get Junior's lock!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.86,0:09:02.73,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.96,0:09:05.76,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Darn. And I wanted\Nto dance with Asuka.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.00,0:09:07.16,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,You've got to be kidding.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.47,0:09:08.96,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,What did you put in there?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.48,0:09:14.54,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Oh, just something\NI didn't want to get stolen.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.99,0:09:17.12,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,What on earth are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.96,0:09:21.62,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Wow. I let a girl catch me off guard.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.64,0:09:26.07,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure he was after\Nanother of his silly stories.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.31,0:09:28.44,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Aha. So the film's...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.15,0:09:30.74,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,in my locker.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.06,0:09:37.90,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,What are you going to do\Nwith the lock, anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.67,0:09:41.57,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Oh, nothing in particular.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.01,0:09:44.38,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,So, will you let me remove your lock?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.55,0:09:46.02,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,What? Yeah, sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.39,0:09:49.48,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Oh, no!\NYou're going to give it to her!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.36,0:09:53.26,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,On second thought, you can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.94,0:09:55.91,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Hey, why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.48,0:09:58.27,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Could it be?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.15,0:10:02.05,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,I kinda forgot the combination.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.99,0:10:05.89,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Where'd they go?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.19,0:10:26.15,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Saint Paulia School Festival
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.98,0:10:48.45,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,The preparations took forever,\Nbut once it got started...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.48,0:10:49.95,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,time passed so quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.02,0:10:52.55,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,It sure did. It's almost getting dark.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.16,0:10:54.42,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Where's Meimi?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.07,0:10:57.06,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Now that you mention it, where is she?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.20,0:10:59.19,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,She's goofing off somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.48,0:11:04.85,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Lord forgive me,\Nfor I use no gimmick or trick.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.20,0:11:11.13,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,One!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.57,0:11:14.54,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Two!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.84,0:11:18.04,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Three!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.41,0:11:38.25,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,May the blessings of God be with us!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.76,0:11:41.92,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,It's getting dark. Isn't it almost time?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.73,0:11:44.79,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,They said it's the real St. Tail.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.94,0:11:46.27,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,You're kidding!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.75,0:11:54.95,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Eek! It's St. Tail!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.29,0:11:57.42,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Over there?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.00,0:12:00.83,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.71,0:12:05.80,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,I'm not letting you get away today!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.79,0:12:12.62,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,So, there you are, St. Tail!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.36,0:12:14.85,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.84,0:12:20.64,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,We're the St. Tail trio!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.65,0:12:24.98,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,St. Tail's in the 2-A classroom!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.25,0:12:26.12,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,What was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.50,0:12:32.36,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,She had a lot of nerve,\Nappearing in MY class.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.92,0:12:41.32,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Eek! St. Tail's\Nin the audiovisual room!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.09,0:12:43.35,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.43,0:12:44.65,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Darn!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.10,0:12:47.53,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,St. Tail's in the connecting walkway!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.70,0:12:48.86,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.64,0:12:50.87,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Oops!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.91,0:12:54.00,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Darn you, St. Tail!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.12,0:12:56.74,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Is this where you are, Saint Tail?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.82,0:13:00.76,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Hurry up and Join!\NOne Million Saint Tails Planned.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.40,0:13:03.49,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Yes it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.87,0:13:06.80,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Give me a break!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.31,0:13:10.40,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Stop dressing everyone\Nup like St. Tail!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.95,0:13:12.94,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Spoilsport.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.02,0:13:14.82,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Every girl in school!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.99,0:13:17.05,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Hey, isn't that St. Tail?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.56,0:13:17.93,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Where?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.10,0:13:20.09,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Where's St. Tail?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.47,0:13:38.46,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Our decoy operation was a success.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.78,0:13:40.27,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Everyone's gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.94,0:13:55.60,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,The film's mine now.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.71,0:13:59.44,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,The festival's finale will soon begin.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.82,0:14:01.72,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,The festival's finale will soon begin.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.89,0:14:03.15,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,All those interested in\Nparticipating please change...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.29,0:14:05.28,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,and assemble on the school grounds.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.43,0:14:07.16,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,I want this lock.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.37,0:14:11.53,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Sure, it's just a silly superstition,\Nbut what if it does come true?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.74,0:14:12.73,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Hold it right there!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.45,0:14:14.97,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,St. Tail!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.69,0:14:18.31,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,You thought everyone was out\Non the grounds, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.79,0:14:20.45,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,But you couldn't fool me!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.93,0:14:22.12,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Asuka Jr.!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.30,0:14:23.82,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Don't move!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.30,0:14:27.20,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,And don't forget me,\Nhand over the film, you little thief!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.76,0:14:37.63,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,One, two, three!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.92,0:14:47.65,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,What's this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.99,0:14:52.65,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Geez! Asuka, what's going on here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.07,0:14:56.33,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,You're playing dirty, St. Tail!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.18,0:15:04.08,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Would you mind... if I took this lock?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.32,0:15:06.15,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,What the heck are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.23,0:15:10.03,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Take it for all I care, just\Ncome out and fight fair and square!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.64,0:15:12.83,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.67,0:15:30.40,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Let's see, the east side is...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.93,0:15:40.02,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Perfect!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.50,0:15:41.59,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,St. Tail!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.07,0:15:44.54,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Now you'll get yours!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.21,0:15:46.61,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,It's St. Tail!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.94,0:15:47.81,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Where?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.38,0:15:49.47,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.10,0:15:59.23,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,It's the real thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.57,0:16:00.70,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,You're kidding, really?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.11,0:16:04.04,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,I'm trapped!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.45,0:16:06.75,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,There's nowhere to go!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.85,0:16:08.51,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Give me back my film!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.88,0:16:21.04,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Ladies and gentlemen!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.25,0:16:23.24,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Please forgive this commotion!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.26,0:16:28.49,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,What is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.60,0:16:29.59,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,A balloon?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.30,0:16:32.10,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Someone's floating up there.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.24,0:16:33.83,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,And in a bag, no less.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.41,0:16:36.00,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,It's Junior-in-a-bag. And...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.25,0:16:37.65,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Sawatari-in-a-bag!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.33,0:16:43.82,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,You idiots!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.03,0:16:46.56,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Don't just stand there like dummies!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.64,0:16:48.87,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,St. Tail, put us down!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.04,0:16:51.77,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,One, two, three!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.48,0:16:55.54,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,St. Tail disappeared!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.93,0:17:04.73,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Junior and Sawatari have also...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.07,0:17:06.06,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,disappeared.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.96,0:17:15.43,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,I return this to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.43,0:17:16.45,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Oh, the film!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.50,0:17:19.66,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.01,0:17:24.07,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,We did it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.19,0:17:27.98,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.60,0:17:32.65,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Asuka!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.90,0:17:34.39,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,How'd you do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.04,0:17:37.60,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Uh, she did it again.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.05,0:17:40.98,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Miss Haneoka.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.49,0:17:43.21,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Are you alone?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.62,0:17:44.45,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.56,0:17:48.05,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Will you dance with me?\NIt's no fun dancing by yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.23,0:17:50.32,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,I... um... no, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.64,0:17:52.66,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,But why not? Come on, let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.91,0:17:54.47,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,But, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.25,0:17:58.68,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,What'll I do?\NI was going to ask Asuka Jr.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.79,0:17:59.22,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Hold it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.09,0:18:03.08,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,I said hold it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.80,0:18:07.33,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Ouch!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.34,0:18:12.28,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Hey! What's going on here?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.82,0:18:17.38,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,I... but... it hurts,\Nyou don't have to pull so hard!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.29,0:18:19.66,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,You'd better explain that!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.83,0:18:23.10,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,You're always whacking\Nme with a broom...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.24,0:18:25.50,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,so why couldn't you tell\Nhim to back off there?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.24,0:18:29.01,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,If you didn't want to go,\Nyou should have made it clear!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.65,0:18:30.91,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.81,0:18:46.44,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Oh, you don't hate me, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.39,0:18:49.38,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,The charm...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.89,0:19:03.32,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,it actually worked!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.17,0:19:16.44,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Rats! Darn that St. Tail!\NI'll make you pay for this!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.72,0:19:20.19,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Ouch!
